        question: "What are the different windows offered by Eternia?",
        answer: "Eternia offers aluminium windows and doors of every type, size and colour. Our main offerings include: Sliding aluminium windows and doors, Openable/casement aluminium windows and doors. We also offer aluminium windows and doors for all rooms, including living rooms, kitchens and bedrooms. Our aluminium windows and doors can be classified into Duraslim Edge, Duraslim and Essentials - which are three ranges of high-quality products designed to ensure that every Indian home can have true aluminium windows."
